            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New <sic>Yook</sic></placeName>
                <date>July 21<hi rend="sup">st</hi> 5614</date>.</p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>42 Oliver <sic>street</sic></placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N. Y.</placeName>
                <date>July 21, 1854</date>-</p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>, <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p>Peace, as usual:</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Please send me the year's “Occident” from <date>April 1853</date> to<lb/>
                <date>April 1854</date>, along with your deliver of next <date>August</date>,
                through <persName>Mr. Cantor</persName>,<lb/>
                <placeName>56 Duane Street</placeName>. If I should not sell it, I will return it to
                you<lb/> cost free. AS to news, the rumour is current here that <persName>Dr.
                    Illoway</persName><lb/> will deliver his trial sermon at the Broadway synagogue
                in <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>,<lb/> on <date>Sabbath Nahamu</date>.*</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">With every respect and friendship,</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>42 Oliver Street</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>*The <date>Sabbath Nahamu</date> is the one immediately after <date>Tish'a
                    b-av</date></p>
        </body>
